%description
Provides functions to calculate indicators for four marine ecosystem
attributes (Biodiversity, Ecosystem Structure and Functioning, Ecosystem
Stability and Resistance to Perturbations, Resource Potential) and one
marine ecosystem pressure (Fishing Pressure) from fishery independent
trawl survey data and commercial landings data. All indicators were
selected and evaluated using the “Indicator Selection Guidance Framework”
developed by Bundy, Gomez, and Cook (2017, ISBN: 978-0-660-23573-8).

